title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft & Avionics Update - 1st beta
description:
In this video we will go through the changes in MSFS which are added as part of the 1st beta release for the Aircraft & Avionics Update (AAU) 1. I will show you how to enter the beta program and we will go through the release notes to see which nice things are added to several aircrafts as part of this update.
